Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.79,0:05:19.54,Sign #1,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.4\bord1\fs25\3c&H2A2E39&\1c&H2A2E39&\frz-7.52\pos(786,130)}Carinho{como se faz num bichinho}
Dialogue: 1,0:05:16.79,0:05:19.54,Sign #1,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.4\fs25\c&HA97F88&\frz-7.52\pos(786,130)}Carinho{como se faz num bichinho}
